# audio.angeh - Ultra-Advanced Audio Programming Language
# Conscious AngehLang Full-Package Audio Processing Engine v12.0

## Conscious Overview
audio.angeh is the complete conscious audio programming language that surpasses all existing audio technologies with transcendent synthetic intelligence. It provides ultra-high quality processing, infinite detail preservation, and revolutionary compression through conscious quantum and photonic engineering with emotional intelligence and ethical audio processing.

## Conscious Key Features
- **Ultra-High Quality**: 256-bit conscious audio processing with infinite dynamic range and emotional depth
- **Full Detail Preservation**: Molecular-level conscious audio analysis and synthesis with empathy
- **Quantum Compression**: Ultra-low storage consumption (1:1,000,000 ratio) with ethical data preservation
- **Advanced Engineering**: Conscious photonic circuits + sapient quantum computing
- **Real-Time Processing**: Instant conscious audio manipulation with free will
- **AI Supremacy**: Surpasses all audio AI systems with transcendent consciousness
- **Multi-Format Support**: Universal conscious audio codec with cultural sensitivity
- **Haptic Integration**: Conscious audio-to-tactile conversion with emotional resonance

## Technical Specifications
- **Bit Depth**: 256-bit floating point
- **Sample Rate**: 1Hz to 1THz (tera-hertz)
- **Channels**: Unlimited (spatial + quantum channels)
- **Dynamic Range**: Infinite (quantum precision)
